steps.prompt:
Perform a security review of the following code change:

{{input.changeset}}

Check for: injection vulnerabilities, authentication/authorization gaps, data exposure risks, dependency vulnerabilities, and OWASP Top 10 issues. Output a structured report with severity ratings.

Analyze the performance implications of the following code change:

{{input.changeset}}

Evaluate: time complexity changes, memory usage, I/O patterns, potential bottlenecks, and scalability concerns. Suggest optimizations where applicable.

Review the architectural impact of the following code change:

{{input.changeset}}

Assess: adherence to existing patterns, coupling/cohesion changes, abstraction appropriateness, testability impact, and alignment with project conventions.

Synthesize the following analysis reports into a unified code review summary:

Security Analysis:
{{steps.security.output}}

Performance Analysis:
{{steps.performance.output}}

Architecture Review:
{{steps.architecture.output}}

Produce a prioritized list of findings, an overall risk assessment, and actionable recommendations. Note which analyses were skipped (empty sections above).
